node.text:
.
.
.
Do you like fathead dough or nah?! 🤔 
.
.
Ingredients:
4 hot dogs (cut in half length wise)
1 1/2 cup shredded mozzarella 
2 tbsp cream cheese
1 cup almond flour 
1 large egg (whisked)
Seasonings of your choice 
.
.
Instructions:
1. Mix cream cheese and mozzarella. Microwave for 1 minute.
2. Stir and microwave for 30 more seconds. Stir again. Add your whisked egg & almond flour. Mix. 
3. Add your seasonings and mix again.
4. Knead and flatten out between two sheets of greased parchment paper. 
5. Cut into 2x2 inch rectangles, add your hot dogs and roll them up.
6. Air fry at 400F for 6-8 minutes flipping halfway through.
.
.
#keto #lowcarb #ketorecipes

node.text:
.
.
.
To make it just add sliced avocado between two layers of shredded Mexican cheese in your waffle maker and close for 3-5 minutes. 
.
.
It will smoke a lot that’s okay! And if you try to take it out too early the top will stick to the waffle maker so wait until the top easily opens before taking them out.
.
.
For the Aji Verde sauce @anafioreo just posted the recipe 😋
.
.
#keto #lowcarb #ketodiet #chaffles #chaffle

node.text:
.
.
.
Ingredients:
Shredded cheddar
1 large egg
Toppings of your choice
.
.
Instructions:
1. On medium low heat, add cheddar to a pan and clear out a circle in the middle. 
3. Add your egg to the circle. Season and add your toppings. 
4. Add more cheese and cover with a lid for 1-2 minutes.
5. Remove lid and flip for 1-2 more minutes. Take off and enjoy!
.
.

node.text:
.
.
.
Ingredients:
6 tbsp almond flour (or 1.5 tbsp coconut flour)
1 cup sliced strawberries 
1 large egg
2 tbsp butter
2 tbsp sweetener 
1 tsp vanilla
1/4 tsp baking powder 
Whipped cream
.
.
Instructions:
1. Melt butter in a mug and combine with all ingredients except strawberries & whipped cream.
2. Microwave for 90 seconds until firm, dump on a plate, let cool & cut in half horizontally.
3. Add strawberries to the middle, then top with more strawberries & whipped cream! 
.
.
#keto #ketorecipes #lowcarb #mugcake

node.title: Say “YES” if you would eat this strawberry shortcake 🙌🍓😋

node.text:
.
.
.
An amazing dinner by @anafioreo 😋
.
.
Cauliflower risotto ingredients:
1 Tbsp butter
3 cloves of minced garlic 
1/4 cup chopped white onion
1 lb cauliflower rice (cooked and strained well)
1/2 cup of heavy cream
1 cups grated Parmesan 
.
.
Instructions:
	1.	Combine butter with garlic and onions on medium low until fragrant. 
	2.	Add in the cauliflower rice until it softens.
	3.	Add heavy cream, parmesan, & seasonings.
	4.	Cook for 5-7 minutes.
.
.
Bruschetta ingredients:
4 chopped Roma tomato 
1/2 onion chopped finely 
2 cloves of minced garlic
1/2 cup fresh mozzarella 
1/4 cup chopped basil 
1/4 cup grated Parmesan 
2 Tbsp olive oil 
Salt
Pepper 
.
.
Instructions:
	1.	Combine all ingredients and add over grilled chicken breast. 
.
.
#ketorecipes #lowcarb #ketodiet

node.title: Say “YES” if you would eat this Chicken Bruschetta with Cauliflower Rissoto

node.text:
.
.
.
Do you like fathead dough or nah?! 🤔 
.
.
Ingredients:
4 hot dogs (cut in half length wise)
1 1/2 cup shredded mozzarella 
2 tbsp cream cheese
1 cup almond flour 
1 large egg (whisked)
Seasonings of your choice 
.
.
Instructions:
1. Mix cream cheese and mozzarella. Microwave for 1 minute.
2. Stir and microwave for 30 more seconds. Stir again. Add your whisked egg & almond flour. Mix. 
3. Add your seasonings and mix again.
4. Knead and flatten out between two sheets of greased parchment paper. 
5. Cut into 2x2 inch rectangles, add your hot dogs and roll them up.
6. Air fry at 400F for 6-8 minutes flipping halfway through.
.
.
#keto #lowcarb #ketorecipes

.
.
To make it just add sliced avocado between two layers of shredded Mexican cheese in your waffle maker and close for 3-5 minutes. 
.
.
It will smoke a lot that’s okay! And if you try to take it out too early the top will stick to the waffle maker so wait until the top easily opens before taking them out.
.
.
For the Aji Verde sauce @anafioreo just posted the recipe 😋
.
.
#keto #lowcarb #ketodiet #chaffles #chaffle

node.text:
Cheese wrap hack!! What fillings would you add? 😋

To make it just add natural cheese to a non stick pan on medium heat until it gets slightly brown on the edges. Then remove pan from heat, let it cool down for a few mins, add your fillings, roll it up, & enjoy! 

#keto #lowcarb #ketorecipes #cheese
